<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - GearUp</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .about-container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background-color: #212529; /* Dark Grey Background */
            padding: 40px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            border-radius: 10px;
            max-width: 80%;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .about-content {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: justify;
        }

            .about-content h1 {
                color: #d3d3d3;
            }

            .about-content .highlight {
                font-weight: bold;
                color: #FFFFFF;
            }

        .about-image {
            flex: 1;
            text-align: center;
        }

            .about-image img {
                max-width: 100%;
                height: auto;
                border-radius: 10px;
            }

        .stats {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px auto;
            max-width: 80%;
        }

        .stat-box {
            background: #212529; /* Dark Grey Background */
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            width: 30%;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

            .stat-box h2 {
                margin: 0;
                color: #FFFFFF;
                font-size: 28px;
            }

            .stat-box p {
                margin: 5px 0 0;
                color: #FFFFFF;
                font-size: 16px;
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <section class="about-container">
        <div class="about-image">
            <img src="/pics/company.jpg" alt="Team Working">
        </div>
        <div class="about-content">
            <h1>About Us</h1>
            <p class="highlight">Safe, Comprehensive, and Trustworthy Platform</p>
            <p>
                At GearUp, we strive to revolutionize the car rental industry by making vehicle booking seamless, secure, and accessible.
                Our platform is designed to provide an efficient and transparent rental experience for travelers, daily commuters, and businesses alike.
                With an extensive range of well-maintained vehicles, advanced booking options, and customer-friendly policies, we ensure reliability at every step.
                Whether you need a car for a short trip or long-term use, GearUp offers flexible rental solutions tailored to your needs.
                Our mission is to bridge the gap between convenience and affordability, allowing customers to travel with ease.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="stats">
        <div class="stat-box">
            <h2>20,123</h2>
            <p>Happy Customers</p>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-box">
            <h2>1,400</h2>
            <p>Vehicles Available</p>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-box">
            <h2>13,560</h2>
            <p>Bookings Completed</p>
        </div>
    </section>

</body>
</html>
